Tip1 Meet the Dot Command

The dot command lets us repeat the last change. 上次修改可以指很多东西，
一次修改的单位可以是字符、整行、甚至是整个文件.
Origin:

Line one
Line two
Line three
Line four


Line one
Line two
Line three
Line four

'>G' :
'j'. :



Tip2 Don’t Repeat Yourself

origin:
var foo = 1
var bar = 'a'
var foobar = foo + bar

在语句后面添加";",操作如下:
1) 'A;'
2) 'j.'
3) 'j.'

output:
var foo = 1;
var bar = 'a';
var foobar = foo + bar;
